name: Osprey Transporter Wheeled Carry On - Unisex
description: Elegantly constructed with durable, high-quality materials, this wheeled carry-on is replete with easy-to-access compartments and organizing features that will satisfy the most detail-oriented traveller. It's built to accommodate as much as possible while remaining within most domestic airline carry-on standards. Oversized wheels roll smoothly on airport tile and tarmac, with a high-clearance chassis to tackle cobbles and rough surfaces.Rugged nylon fabric is TPU-coated for added water resistance.Nylon packcloth base is highly abrasion resistant.Side-opening main compartment.External zip access to main toiletries compartment.Zippered back panel pocket offers extra storage.Hidden RFID security pocket protects your wallet and passport.Padded sleeve accommodates laptops up to 15in.Internal main compartment has compression panels and a mesh closure to keep your clothes neatly in place.Padded top and side handles.Collapsible single pole handle is made from high quality 6061 series aluminum.Aluminum tube foot also serves as a grab handle when unloading from overhead compartment.90mm wheels on Osprey's high clearance chassis.
